    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes mechanical function over cosmetic perfection. The engine and transmission are solid, but the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some clear coat peeling on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets. It has been recently serviced and is ready to drive, though it could benefit from some aesthetic TLC in the future.",
